&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;strong&gt;high-impact, high-visibility role&lt;/strong&gt; reporting directly to the Head of Partnerships, APAC, with strategic influence over APAC&#39;s fast-growing corridor of opportunities. You&#39;ll be a key driver for Payoneer&#39;s market leadership in Singapore, building a world-class partnership ecosystem to capture partner growth &amp;amp; customer acquisition within APAC.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;seasoned partnerships professional with proven Singapore CSP (Corporate Service Provider) network&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;with a strong quota carrying commercial background&lt;/strong&gt;, who brings established relationships and competitive intelligence to accelerate market penetration. Someone comfortable engaging with CSP executives at C-level, navigating complex partnership negotiations, and driving systematic revenue growth in a competitive, fast-paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU WILL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CSP Partnership Acquisition&lt;/strong&gt;: Systematically build a Hunting Motion for Singapore CSP partnerships with tier-1 and tier-2 providers including &lt;strong&gt;Enterprise, Mid-Market CSPs&lt;/strong&gt;, &amp;amp; Regional/Local Specialized CSPs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive Displacement Strategy&lt;/strong&gt;: Execute targeted initiatives to displace competitors and other fintech incumbents through:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Superior value proposition development (pricing, product features, service quality)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relationship-based competitive intelligence gathering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic CSP partnership negotiations leveraging competitor pain points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Development&lt;/strong&gt;: Build and manage a robust CSP partnership funnel of new partnerships, tracking from initial outreach to partnership agreement execution to revenue ramp&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partnership Agreements&lt;/strong&gt;: Lead commercial negotiations for partnership terms, referral fee structures, SLAs, and co-marketing commitments with CSP partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enablement &amp;amp; Training&lt;/strong&gt;: Develop CSP partner enablement materials, conduct training sessions on Payoneer value proposition, and ensure partners can articulate differentiation vs. competitors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Management&lt;/strong&gt;: Analyze partnership performance data (referral volume, conversion rates, customer LTV) and optimize underperforming partnerships through targeted interventions&lt;/li

